title: 5 Bdrm/2 Bath House Next to Concordia University
posting_body: ['This modernized, old-fashioned house is located super close to Concordia University.', 'The original woodwork is detailed beautifully and it features hardwood floors throughout, spacious closets, a fully-equipped kitchen, washer & dryer in-unit, grand windows for plenty of natural sunlight, & off-street parking.', 'Pet friendly.', 'Renters are to set up and manage all utilities.', 'One time administrative fee of $25/adult to set up an online portal to pay rent, submit maintenance requests, receive important notices and view your account from anywhere.', 'Our Summer special is no monthly pet rent or pet deposit as well as a waived application fee and 50% off the security deposit.', 'This 5 bedroom single family house is available for immediate move-in.', ' The lease will go until May 26th, 2023.', 'For further inquires or to set up a tour, contact Marisa at 612.500.3four2six.', 'Texting preferred.']
